sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as Domain Agent
    participant Registry as Tool Registry
    participant Cache as Cache Layer
    participant Adapter as Tool Adapter
    participant DB as Databricks API
    participant Events as Event Stream
    
    Note over Agent,Events: Simplified Tool Execution Flow
    
    Agent->>Registry: execute_tool("resolve_query", params)
    Registry->>Events: ToolStartEvent
    Events-->>Agent: (stream)
    
    Registry->>Registry: Validate Parameters
    
    Registry->>Cache: Check Cache
    
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>Registry: Cached Result
        Registry->>Events: ToolEndEvent (cached)
    else Cache Miss
        Cache-->>Registry: Not Cached
        
        Registry->>Adapter: Execute Tool
        Note over Adapter: Domain Logic<br/>+ Service Layer
        
        Adapter->>DB: API Call
        
        alt Success
            DB-->>Adapter: Response Data
            Adapter->>Adapter: Transform to Domain Model
            Adapter-->>Registry: Result
            
            Registry->>Cache: Store Result (5min TTL)
            Registry->>Events: ToolEndEvent (success)
            
        else API Error
            DB-->>Adapter: Error Response
            Adapter-->>Registry: ToolExecutionError
            Registry->>Events: ToolEndEvent (error)
        end
    end
    
    Events-->>Agent: (stream)
    Registry-->>Agent: Final Result
    
    Note over Agent: Process result and<br/>continue reasoning

